name: DMD tools
tagline: Tools for computing variants of Dynamic Mode Decomposition
body:
### Welcome
This project provides a collection of tools useful for computing several variants of Dynamic Mode Decomposition.  It is a work in progress, and does not really contain any information yet...

Ideally, one would like to be able to say
```python
import dmdtools
dmdtools.write_paper(data)
```
but we are not there yet.
